org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.languages.common.profile.Codegen

Interface Project

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProjectImpl

    public interface Project
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Project'. Control how code is generated: - name of project to generate code into - target folder within that project (e.g. src-gen) - Batch vs. incremental - Prefix: namespace prefix of generated code (similar to prefix option in genmodel)

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Model
    • Generation Mode
    • Project Name
    • Source Folder
    • Prefix
    See Also:
    CodegenPackage.getProject()
